title: Intervention S01E06 - Travis and Matt
description: Travis, a meth addict and member of Days of the New, a band that makes music, and Matt, a crack-cocaine addict with terrible teeth, are showcased in this episode of Intervention. Travis crumbles under the weight of his own success, leaving his girlfriend to raise their child alone. Matt, once the favorite son, cannot seem to leave crack-cocaine behind to live a fruitful life. Watch the dentures, dreadlocks, and despair of Intervention, Season 1, Episode 6.
